data.description: Immaculate, well cared for LARGE split entry with 4 bedrooms and 3 baths. Complete with attached 2 car garage and fully fenced in backyard. Notably, the home features room additions on both the main and lower levels, providing an abundance of space. The lower level is fully finished and includes a walkout.  New siding, concrete, roof, gutters, downspouts, exterior/interior paint and carpet. A beautiful, updated kitchen, that includes a stylish backsplash, LED under cabinet lighting, pendant lights above the sink and modern high-quality appliances. A cozy family room features a gas fireplace with a remote control. Sliding doors from the family room open to a large deck. The bathrooms have been tastefully renovated, adding to the home's overall appeal.  Pella windows throughout. Centrally situated in the desirable Millard neighborhood, you'll enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping and have all levels of schooling close to home.
